    "content": "<p>人物模型变大，两种方法，一种是nut获取角色ani，第二种就是用台服自带的ACT<br />\n下面就是第二种方法<br />\n自带的变大obj，编号：16047</p>\n\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://book.tiansj.net//server/index.php?s=/api/attachment/visitFile&amp;sign=e090e3a064a7dfa4279129065abc3056\" /><img alt=\"\" height=\"477\" src=\"/media/uploads/2023/07/06/1.jpg\" width=\"748\" /></p>\n\n<p><img alt=\"\" height=\"834\" src=\"/media/uploads/2023/07/06/2.jpg\" width=\"800\" /><br />\n<img alt=\"\" src=\"http://book.tiansj.net//server/index.php?s=/api/attachment/visitFile&amp;sign=0aaba4ac5591f18af7b8a2cfe90f7df9\" /></p>\n\n<p>接下来开始换思路了，让这个obj可以打自己，在obj里修改atk攻击数据</p>\n\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://book.tiansj.net//server/index.php?s=/api/attachment/visitFile&amp;sign=dddd71a312b093dfffbfefc1ccf7ede3\" /><img alt=\"\" height=\"440\" src=\"/media/uploads/2023/07/06/3.jpg\" width=\"702\" /><br />\n<img alt=\"\" src=\"http://book.tiansj.net//server/index.php?s=/api/attachment/visitFile&amp;sign=a3669bb3f66a91d8b16733c867eec12d\" />[attack friend]修改为[attack myself]<br />\n<img alt=\"\" src=\"http://book.tiansj.net//server/index.php?s=/api/attachment/visitFile&amp;sign=9f133bc859f18eca56829650d49b40cb\" /><img alt=\"\" height=\"419\" src=\"/media/uploads/2023/07/06/4.jpg\" width=\"800\" /></p>\n\n<p><img alt=\"\" height=\"428\" src=\"/media/uploads/2023/07/06/5.jpg\" width=\"767\" /></p>\n\n<p><img alt=\"\" height=\"454\" src=\"/media/uploads/2023/07/06/6.jpg\" width=\"800\" /><br />\n<img alt=\"\" src=\"http://book.tiansj.net//server/index.php?s=/api/attachment/visitFile&amp;sign=7ba765ab5d279e268e33fa98213e2cca\" /></p>\n\n<p>保存一下PVF，上游戏，进图给自己创建16047obj，打自己就可以变大了<br />\n<img alt=\"\" src=\"http://book.tiansj.net//server/index.php?s=/api/attachment/visitFile&amp;sign=11ebcd6fcd1367a700149e6407103cbc\" /></p>\n\n<p><img alt=\"\" height=\"472\" src=\"/media/uploads/2023/07/06/1.gif\" width=\"631\" /></p>\n\n<p>@老徐的梦想8</p>\n",
